 <!-- Regional Manufacturing Hubs -->
 <section id="regions" class="mb-16">
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">5. Which Manufacturing Hub Is Best for Power Banks?</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Your choice of power bank supplier location impacts cost, speed, and quality. Here is how the three main hubs compare:</p>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
 <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200">
 <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-3">Shenzhen</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">The biggest electronics hub in the world. Shenzhen offers the fastest prototyping (48-hour PCB), the widest parts access, and the most skilled R&D engineers. Labor costs are highest here but still competitive globally.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Best for:</strong> Custom OEM projects, fast prototyping, premium products, complex designs. WOWOHCOOL is based here, with 24-hour engineering support and same-day part sourcing.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200">
 <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-3">Dongguan</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Home to massive factories with lower land and labor costs. Dongguan is the manufacturing backbone of the Pearl River Delta. It has hundreds of mid-to-large battery and power bank factories with a strong PCB and molding supply chain.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Best for:</strong> High-volume runs, cost-sensitive projects, established designs. Good when you need scale without Shenzhen prices.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200">
 <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-3">Guangzhou</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">A growing hub with more battery and accessory factories. Guangzhou offers pricing between Shenzhen and Dongguan, with good port access for export. The Canton Fair (held here twice a year) is a natural meeting point for global buyers.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Best for:</strong> Mid-volume production, export ease, Canton Fair sourcing. Good for brands that value logistics speed.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange p-4 rounded-r-xl mt-6">
 <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm italic"><strong>Insider Tip:</strong> Many Shenzhen makers (including WOWOHCOOL) have extra lines in Dongguan for big orders. This gives you Shenzhen R&D speed with Dongguan's low costs at scale.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

