 <!-- Beyond Power Banks -->
 <section id="beyond-power-banks" class="mb-16">
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">6. Beyond Power Banks: Top Charger Manufacturers in China</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">If you are sourcing power banks from China, chances are you also need GaN chargers, wireless chargers, or car chargers. The good news: most power bank factories already produce these products on shared SMT lines and use the same battery management and power delivery engineering teams.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Why the overlap? Power banks and wall chargers share core technologies — PD/QC protocol ICs, GaN switching transistors, thermal management, and safety certification processes. A factory that builds 140W PD 3.1 power banks already has the GaN expertise, PCB layout skills, and UL/CE test infrastructure to produce matching wall chargers and car chargers. For B2B buyers, this means <strong>one supplier, one audit, multiple product lines</strong> — reducing lead time and compliance costs by 30-40%.</p>
 <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-brandBlue mb-4">Key Charger Manufacturers Also Producing Power Banks</h3>
 <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-slate-600 mb-8">
 <li><strong>WOWOHCOOL</strong> — Full-range charging ecosystem: <a href="/products/gan-charger/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">GaN chargers (35W-140W)</a>, <a href="/products/wireless-charger/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">Qi2 wireless chargers</a>, <a href="/products/car-charger/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">MagSafe car mounts</a>, and power banks spanning <a href="/products/power-bank/semi-solid-state/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">semi-solid-state</a>, <a href="/products/power-bank/2-in-1-hybrid/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">2-in-1 hybrid chargers</a>, and <a href="/products/power-bank/smart-display/" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">TFT smart display</a> models. Single-source OEM with MOQ 500 across all categories.</li>
 <li><strong>Anker Innovations</strong> — GaNPrime wall chargers (up to 150W), PowerWave wireless pads, and car charger lines. High MOQ (10,000+) but unmatched brand recognition for retail partnerships.</li>
 <li><strong>Baseus</strong> — Known for 65W-100W GaN chargers with integrated cables, 15W MagSafe wireless chargers, and compact car chargers. Strong industrial design team for ODM projects.</li>
 <li><strong>Huntkey Group</strong> — Enterprise-grade USB-C chargers, multi-port GaN stations, and certified car chargers for automotive OEMs. ISO 14001 environmental certification for EU market compliance.</li>
 <li><strong>Aohai Technology</strong> — Rugged car chargers (IP67), outdoor solar charging panels, and industrial-grade GaN adapters for harsh environments.</li>
